object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = '$$batch_status_inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = '$$batch_status_inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT
metal_arp.source_name,
metal_arp.load_type,
metal_arp.id,
metal_arp.role_name,
metal_arp.permission_name,
current_batch.batch_id,
bronze_arp.adm_role_permissions_row_id as role_permissions_row_id,
bronze_arp.adm_role_permissions_md5checksum as role_permissions_md5checksum,
bronze_arp.adm_role_permissions_row_effective_end_datetime as role_permissions_row_effective_datetime,
bronze_arp.adm_role_permissions_batch_id as role_permissions_batch_id,
bronze_arp.id as role_permissions_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_role_permissions metal_arp
left outer join $$staging_schema.adm_role_permissions bronze_arp
on metal_arp.id = bronze_arp.id
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
metal_arp.id
